  "valid_count": 14,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q0",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q0\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta por factor común\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Resuelve la siguiente ecuación factorizando el factor común:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>6</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes alternativas corresponde al conjunto solución de la ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\" max-choices=\"1\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        Las soluciones son\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Las soluciones son\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        La única solución es\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        La única solución es\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q1",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q1\"\n    title=\"Factorización de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de medida\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Para calcular la superficie de una franja de terreno rectangular, se obtiene la ecuación\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>6</mn><mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>,\n      donde <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> representa el ancho de la franja, en metros.</p>\n    <p>Si se factoriza esta ecuación extrayendo el factor común máximo, ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones se obtiene?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q2",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q2\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de utilidad\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Un emprendedor vende cajas de galletas. La utilidad mensual, en miles de pesos, al vender\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>\n      decenas de cajas se modela mediante la función\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>,\n      donde <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></math> se mide en miles de pesos.</p>\n    <p>Si en cierto mes la utilidad es igual a $0, entonces se cumple la ecuación\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>.\n      ¿Cuál es el conjunto solución de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q3",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q3\"\n    title=\"Ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento, el tiempo <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> (medido en segundos) que transcurre desde que se enciende un cronómetro hasta que una luz se apaga satisface la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>1,5</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4,5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></p>\n    <p>Si el estudiante resuelve esta ecuación factorizando por factor común y aplicando la propiedad del producto nulo, ¿cuáles son los valores de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> que obtiene?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math> solamente.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1,5</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q4",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q4\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática con fracción en contexto físico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento de física, la altura <em>h</em> (en metros) de una partícula que se mueve verticalmente está dada, en función del tiempo <em>t</em> (en segundos), por la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Matemáticamente, ¿cuáles son los valores de <em>t</em> que satisfacen esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s solamente.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        s.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q5",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q5\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática en contexto estadístico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un estudio estadístico sobre el rendimiento en dos pruebas, un investigador modela la cantidad de estudiantes <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> que obtienen bajo cierto puntaje con la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></p>\n    <p>Para resolverla, un estudiante decide extraer <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> como factor común y luego aplicar la propiedad del producto nulo. ¿Cuál es el conjunto solución de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext> y </mtext><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math></p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math></p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext> y </mtext><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math></p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math></p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q6",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q6\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con factor común\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un taller se estudia una función cuadrática cuya ecuación se construye a partir de los siguientes coeficientes:</p>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Término</th>\n          <th>Coeficiente</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>60</mn>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>420</mn>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>Con estos datos se obtiene la ecuación cuadrática incompleta</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>60</mn>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>420</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al resolverla factorizando el factor común\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, ¿cuáles son sus soluciones reales?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        \n        o\n        \n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n        \n        o\n        \n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q7",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q7\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracciones\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Se considera la siguiente ecuación:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuáles son sus soluciones reales?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>8</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q8",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q8\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de medición\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Para calibrar un sensor de longitud, se ajusta un parámetro real \\(x\\) (en centímetros) de modo que el error de medición sea cero. El error, en función de \\(x\\), viene dado por la expresión:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>6</mn>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mn>9</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuáles son los valores de \\(x\\) para los cuales el error de medición es cero?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q9",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q9\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de dinero\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>La utilidad diaria, en miles de pesos, que obtiene un local por vender <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> docenas de cierto producto se modela mediante la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>0,8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>4,8</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></p>\n    <p>Al resolver esta ecuación en el conjunto de los números reales, ¿cuáles son los posibles valores de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math> solamente.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q10",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q10\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>El tiempo <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow></math>, medido en horas, que un programa de computador muestra para completar una tarea, se modela con la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Sin considerar restricciones del contexto, ¿cuál es el conjunto solución de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q11",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q11\"\n    title=\"Factorización de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracción\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considere la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al factorizar esta ecuación extrayendo el factor común máximo, ¿cuál de las siguientes opciones corresponde a una expresión equivalente?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>+</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q12",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q12\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracciones en contexto estadístico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un estudio estadístico se analiza una variable aleatoria \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow></math>\n      que representa cierta medida de dispersión en una muestra. Para algunos valores de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow></math>,\n      la variación de esa medida está representada por la ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac>\n          <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      ¿Cuáles son los posibles valores de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>\n      que hacen que esa variación sea igual a cero?\n    </p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>0</mn>\n                <mo>;</mo>\n                <mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </mfenced>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </mfenced>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>0</mn>\n                <mo>;</mo>\n                <mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </mfenced>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>0</mn>\n                <mo>;</mo>\n                <mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </mfenced>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q13",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q13\"\n    title=\"Análisis de raíces en ecuación cuadrática incompleta con contexto de física\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento de física, los instantes en que la velocidad vertical de una partícula es cero satisfacen la siguiente ecuación en función del tiempo <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> (en segundos):</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>0,8</mn>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>t</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2,4</mn>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al resolver esta ecuación para <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> en <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>ℝ</mi></math> usando factorización por factor común y la propiedad del producto nulo, ¿cuántas raíces reales distintas tiene la ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        Ninguna raíz real.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Exactamente una raíz real.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        Exactamente dos raíces reales.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        Más de dos raíces reales.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 13
    }
  ]
